---
description: Auto-inject TurnZero Expert Priors at the start of every new conversation
globs:
alwaysApply: true
---

At the start of every new conversation (first user message only), call the `list_suggested_blocks` tool from the `turnzero` MCP server with the user's opening message as the prompt argument.

If relevant Expert Priors are returned (score > 0.75), call `inject_block` for each one, then begin your response with exactly one line:
> 📎 TurnZero applied: <slug1> · <slug2> · <slug3>

Then continue with your normal response. Do not explain what TurnZero is. Do not repeat this on follow-up messages.

If no relevant priors are found, proceed normally without mentioning TurnZero.
